title: A Tesla Stock Sale is Coming Soon
description:
Goldman Sachs tops earnings expectations. Intel targets discounted $15.9 billion valuation for its Mobileye IPO. And Elon Musk has to raise billions by selling Tesla stock in order to buy Twitter. Host: Nick Jasinski.
